title: The Playmates - Golden Classics (320)
description:
The Playmates - Golden Classics (320)
The Playmates - Golden Classics (320)

Beep beep!  Beep beep!  His horn went beep beep beep!

So goes The Playmates' one big hit novelty of 1958.  If you haven't heard it yet, here's your chance.  The rest of the songs aren't as well known but they're equally humorous and worth a listen.

1.  Jo Ann
2.  Let's Be Lovers
3.  Don't Go Home
4.  The Day I Died
5.  While the Record Goes Around and Around
6.  Beep Beep 
7.  Your Love
8.  Star Love
9.  What Is Love?
10. First Love
11. Wait for Me
12. Little Miss Stuck Up
